PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (923) by making provision for an Interim Marketing Authorization that would make it possible to market food that is not in compliance with the Regulations while an amendment to the Regulations to permit its on-going legal sale is being processed.

precis:
Regulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (923) by making
provision for an Interim Marketing Authorization that would make it
possible to market food that is not in compliance with the Regulations
while an amendment to the Regulations to permit its on-going legal sale
is being processed.
